text: "It's Gonna Be Me" is a song by NSYNC. It was taken from their third studio album No Strings Attached. It went to number 1 in both the United States and Canada. It went to the top twenty in Australia, Belgium, Italy, New Zealand, Norway, Scotland, Sweden and the United Kingdom. ==Composition== "It's Gonna Be Me" is written in the key of C minor with a tempo of 82 beats per minute, and based on common time.
